{"tid":622934,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[返工疲勞撚]有無人隻眼會好似我咁？","createTime":"2018-04-09T14:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T15:23:44.000Z","uid":13518,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1e321726a03039586c4420cd2a5433543a7e1b","tid":622934,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"以前仲年輕我曾經為我對眼自豪<br />\n出左黎做野年幾兩年<br />\n黑眼圈愈黎愈重 隻眼又睇落好攰咁 影相都搞到好似我好攰咁<br />\n最近隻眼唔知關唔關返風事 好乾 合埋眼就覺得少少熱添 好攰 有事睇睇下野都唔覺意out fo 即係所謂既放空<br />\n本身無近視都變左有百幾二百度近視<br />\n其實想知係咪睇醫生滴下眼藥水 會對我情況好啲？<br />\n上網search 眼乾 全部都係出乾眼左田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本時已經有用開eye cream 沖完涼都有敷熱毛巾<br />\n有無同路人救救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f0fa4425691f8c0d097734b07260f573e513f9","tid":622934,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:20:20.000Z","msg":"補充多樣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前初初返工都會識恰下眼訓<br />\n而家就算眼訓都唔會恰 頂盡out fo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知搞乜搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0b1b498a5dec9ad4fb3d2a9d603f9ebaa2c3f1","tid":622934,"uid":180173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:29:10.000Z","msg":"望電腦望得好勁？"},{"pid":"5743b6566d0e08ce00b34cd9b0983f7bdb8f3bf8","tid":622934,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d0b1b498a5dec9ad4fb3d2a9d603f9ebaa2c3f1","tid":622934,"uid":180173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:29:10.000Z","msg":"望電腦望得好勁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2